<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to {{ platformName }}!</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #0056b3;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px 0;
    }
    .content p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .credentials {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 15px;
      border: 1px dashed #ddd;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .credentials strong {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 100px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Welcome Aboard, {{ businessName }}!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Hello {{ adminFullName }},</p>
      <p>Congratulations! Your business, <strong>{{ businessName }}</strong>, has been successfully registered on the {{ platformName }} platform.</p>
      <p>You can now log in to your Business Admin portal to manage your loyalty program, members, and services. Here are your initial login credentials:</p>
      <div class="credentials">
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> {{ email }}</p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> {{ password }}</p>
      </div>
      <p>We strongly recommend that you change this password upon your first login.</p>
      <p>To get started, please visit our login page: <a href="{{ loginUrl }}">{{ loginUrl }}</a></p>
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The {{ platformName }} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{ currentYear }} {{ platformName }}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 